<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Struct representing the risk parameters for an algorithm. </para>



<para>This struct is used to represent the risk parameters for an algorithm. The model we use here is called a &quot;Triple Barrier&quot; risk model, where we have a profit taking value, a stop loss value, and a time to live value. </para>
</section>
